effect_entries.effect: Inflicts regular damage.  User takes 1/4 the damage it inflicts in recoil.
effect_entries.short_effect: User receives 1/4 the damage it inflicts in recoil.

flavor_text_entries.flavor_text:
Une charge électrique violente qui blesse
aussi légèrement le lanceur.

The user shrouds itself in electricity
and smashes into its target.
It also damages the user a little.

The user shrouds itself in electricity
and smashes into its target.
It also damages the user a little.

でんきを　まとって
あいてに　ぶつかって　こうげきする。
じぶんも　すこし　ダメージを　うける。

전기를 두르고
상대에게 부딪쳐 공격한다.
자신도 조금 데미지를 입는다.

Une charge électrique violente qui blesse aussi
légèrement le lanceur.

Anwender erzeugt Spannung und greift an,
indem er auf Kollisionskurs geht. Er selbst
erleidet dabei ebenfalls leichten Schaden.

Carga eléctrica muy potente que también hiere
ligeramente a quien la usa.

Chi la usa si carica di elettricità per poi scagliarsi
sul bersaglio, ma subisce dei danni per
il contraccolpo.
